title: using Either for validation
pid: f7fb0069-6687-4948-8054-fcc08546dbdd
body: |2-
  > f = traverseOf (traversed . _2) g where
  |   g x = if x > 0
  |     then Right x
  |     else Left $ "rejected: " ++ show x ++ " is not positive"
  |
  > f [("a",1),("b",2)]
  Right [("a",1),("b",2)]
  > f [("a",1),("b",0)]
  Left "rejected: 0 is not positive"
contains:
- cbd3730c-dcc1-4765-accd-9520cd0ebe9d
